Fourth Department,

October, 1956 * *

(October 31, 1956) The People of the State of New York ex rel. William A. Jackson, Appellant, against Walter B. Martin, as Warden, Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of October 31, 1956, ante, p. 867.-— [Rep.

Motion to appeal on original record and handwritten briefs denied on the ground that the papers fail to show merit to the appeal.
